de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.data

Class DbDataNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.DbObject
      • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.data.DbDataNode

  • public class DbDataNode
extends DbObject
    This class is the representation of a dataNode in the database. It provides the functionality to get all dataObjects belonging to a dataSet as well as the states they can have.
